# Configuration MQTT

## Variables d'environnement

```bash
# Broker MQTT
MQTT_URL=mqtt://tanger.geodaki.com:1883
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=machwatt-module
MQTT_KEEPALIVE=60
MQTT_RECONNECT_PERIOD=5000
MQTT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT=30000
MQTT_QOS=1
MQTT_CLEAN=true

# Topics à écouter (séparés par des virgules)
MQTT_TOPICS=topic/energie,topic/energie3,topic/air,topic/rtls,topic/o2

# Logging
MQTT_LOG_LEVEL=info
MQTT_LOG_MESSAGES=false
```

## Configuration par application

### MACHWATT
```bash
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=machwatt-prod
MQTT_TOPICS=topic/energie,topic/energie3
```

### SiloSense
```bash
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=silosense-prod
MQTT_TOPICS=topic/air,topic/rtls
```

### AirMonitor
```bash
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=airmonitor-prod
MQTT_TOPICS=topic/air
```

### RTLS
```bash
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=rtls-prod
MQTT_TOPICS=topic/rtls
```

### O2Monitor
```bash
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=o2monitor-prod
MQTT_TOPICS=topic/o2
```

## Configuration de production

```bash
# Production
NODE_ENV=production
MQTT_URL=mqtt://tanger.geodaki.com:1883
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=machwatt-prod-${HOSTNAME}
MQTT_KEEPALIVE=60
MQTT_RECONNECT_PERIOD=5000
MQTT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT=30000
MQTT_QOS=1
MQTT_CLEAN=true
MQTT_LOG_LEVEL=warn
```

## Configuration de développement

```bash
# Développement
NODE_ENV=development
MQTT_URL=mqtt://localhost:1883
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=machwatt-dev-${USER}
MQTT_KEEPALIVE=30
MQTT_RECONNECT_PERIOD=1000
MQTT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT=10000
MQTT_QOS=0
MQTT_CLEAN=true
MQTT_LOG_LEVEL=debug
MQTT_LOG_MESSAGES=true
```

## Configuration de test

```bash
# Test
NODE_ENV=test
MQTT_URL=mqtt://test-broker:1883
MQTT_CLIENT_ID=machwatt-test-${RANDOM}
MQTT_KEEPALIVE=30
MQTT_RECONNECT_PERIOD=1000
MQTT_CONNECT_TIMEOUT=5000
MQTT_QOS=0
MQTT_CLEAN=true
MQTT_LOG_LEVEL=silent
MQTT_LOG_MESSAGES=false
```
